articles.title: Prince William's message amid Kate Middleton's recovery hints at her condition - Marca English
articles.description: Prince William dropped a hint about the condition of his wife, Kate Middleton, after she underwent surgery January 17 for an undisclosed abdominal issue at The London Clinic.
